Skills Matrix Status Requirement

- Status must be dynamically generated from `measuredScore` (0-100), not hardcoded.
- Thresholds:
  - `Verified`: score > 70
  - `Needs Evidence`: score >= 50 and <= 70
  - `At Risk`: score < 50
- This mapping must drive both:
  - Per-skill status badge in each row
  - Summary counters for Verified / Needs Evidence / At Risk

Resume Upload/View/Replace Requirement

- Resume uploads must persist in one shared folder: `data/resumes/`.
- All resume upload entry points (profile update dialog and resume analyser dropzone) must write to that same folder.
- Resume section must support:
  - `View`: opens the currently stored resume file from backend.
  - `Replace`: uploads a new file and replaces the previously stored resume for that user.
- Resume metadata (name, updated date, size) must be loaded dynamically from backend storage.
